---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---
<BaseLayout title="YieldRadar - DeFi yield intelligence with multi-factor risk scoring">

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <h1>
      <span class="hero-stat">18,632 yield pools</span> on DeFiLlama.
      Most of them will lose you money.
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      YieldRadar scans them all and pushes the ones worth your attention straight to Telegram.
      No spam. No noise. Only pools that match your exact criteria.
      Updated every 5 minutes.
    </p>
    <a href="https://t.me/yieldradar_bot" class="cta-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      Open in Telegram →
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="why" id="why">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <h2>The problem</h2>
    <p class="lead">
      DeFi has thousands of yield opportunities across dozens of chains.
      Finding the good ones means spending hours on aggregators, checking contracts,
      comparing risk factors — and by the time you find something, the APY has already moved.
    </p>
    <div class="stats-grid">
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat-number">18,632</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Total pools on DeFiLlama</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat-number">~3,800</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Pass our quality filters</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat-number">6</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Chains monitored</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat-number">5 min</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Between full scans</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="how" id="how">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <h2>How it works</h2>
    <div class="pipeline">
      <div class="pipeline-step">
        <div class="step-icon">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/><path d="M12 8v4l3 3"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Fetch</h3>
        <p>Pulls pool data from DeFiLlama every 5 minutes — APY, TVL, 7-day trends, and more.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pipeline-arrow">→</div>
      <div class="pipeline-step">
        <div class="step-icon">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 3H2l8 9.46V19l4 2v-8.54L22 3z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Filter</h3>
        <p>Removes garbage: pools under $500K TVL, outlier APYs, chains you don't care about.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pipeline-arrow">→</div>
      <div class="pipeline-step">
        <div class="step-icon">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6m8 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0h6m0 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Score</h3>
        <p>Multi-factor risk model: APY/volatility, TVL quality, trend, impermanent loss, maturity, GoPlus security audit.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pipeline-arrow">→</div>
      <div class="pipeline-step">
        <div class="step-icon">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M15 17h5l-1.405-1.405A2.032 2.032 0 0118 14.158V11a6.002 6.002 0 00-4-5.659V5a2 2 0 10-4 0v.341C7.67 6.165 6 8.388 6 11v3.159c0 .538-.214 1.055-.595 1.436L4 17h5m6 0v1a3 3 0 11-6 0v-1m6 0H9"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Alert</h3>
        <p>Pushes matching opportunities to Telegram, personalized to your risk tolerance and chain preferences.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="alternatives" id="alternatives">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <h2>Why not just use DeFiLlama?</h2>
    <p class="lead">You can. But here's what happens when you do — and what YieldRadar does differently.</p>
    <div class="alt-grid">
      <div class="alt-row alt-header">
        <span></span>
        <span>DeFiLlama manual</span>
        <span>Alpha Telegram groups</span>
        <span class="alt-us">YieldRadar</span>
      </div>
      <div class="alt-row">
        <span class="alt-feature">Risk scoring</span>
        <span>None</span>
        <span>Opinions only</span>
        <span class="alt-us">6-factor model</span>
      </div>
      <div class="alt-row">
        <span class="alt-feature">Security checks</span>
        <span>Manual</span>
        <span>Rarely</span>
        <span class="alt-us">GoPlus automated</span>
      </div>
      <div class="alt-row">
        <span class="alt-feature">Personalized filters</span>
        <span>Basic</span>
        <span>No</span>
        <span class="alt-us">Chain, risk, TVL, APY</span>
      </div>
      <div class="alt-row">
        <span class="alt-feature">Push notifications</span>
        <span>No</span>
        <span>Spam</span>
        <span class="alt-us">Matched alerts only</span>
      </div>
      <div class="alt-row">
        <span class="alt-feature">Time required</span>
        <span>30 min/day</span>
        <span>Hours of noise</span>
        <span class="alt-us">30 sec setup</span>
      </div>
      <div class="alt-row">
        <span class="alt-feature">Wallet needed?</span>
        <span>No</span>
        <span>No</span>
        <span class="alt-us">No</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="scoring" id="scoring">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <h2>Risk scoring that actually works</h2>
    <p class="lead">
      High APY means nothing if the protocol rugs next week. We score every pool on six factors, not just yield.
    </p>
    <div class="tiers">
      <div class="tier tier-safe">
        <span class="tier-badge">🟢 Safe Yield</span>
        <span class="tier-range">Score 75–100</span>
        <p>Low volatility, high TVL, established protocol, positive trend. The boring ones that make money.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tier tier-watch">
        <span class="tier-badge">🟡 Watch</span>
        <span class="tier-range">Score 50–74</span>
        <p>Decent fundamentals but some risk factors. Worth monitoring, not blindly apeing into.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tier tier-speculative">
        <span class="tier-badge">🟠 Speculative</span>
        <span class="tier-range">Score 25–49</span>
        <p>High APY, higher risk. Newer protocols, volatile yields, or lower TVL. Know what you're getting into.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tier tier-danger">
        <span class="tier-badge">🔴 Danger Zone</span>
        <span class="tier-range">Score 0–24</span>
        <p>Red flags: honeypot patterns, malicious contracts, extreme volatility. We flag these so you don't find out the hard way.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="preview" id="preview">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <h2>What you get</h2>
    <p class="lead">Real examples from live data — not hand-picked marketing.</p>
    <div class="preview-grid">
      <div class="tg-mockup">
        <div class="tg-header">
          <span class="tg-bot-name">YieldRadar Bot</span>
          <span class="tg-verified">✓</span>
        </div>
        <div class="tg-message">
          <p class="tg-pool-name">Aerodrome — USDC-AERO</p>
          <div class="tg-details">
            <div class="tg-detail">
              <span class="tg-label">APY</span>
              <span class="tg-value positive">19.1%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tg-detail">
              <span class="tg-label">TVL</span>
              <span class="tg-value">$22.3M</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tg-detail">
              <span class="tg-label">Risk</span>
              <span class="tg-value watch">🟡 Watch</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tg-detail">
              <span class="tg-label">7d Trend</span>
              <span class="tg-value positive">↑ 2.5%</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tg-meta">Base · LP / Yield Farming</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="tg-mockup">
        <div class="tg-header">
          <span class="tg-bot-name">YieldRadar Bot</span>
          <span class="tg-verified">✓</span>
        </div>
        <div class="tg-message">
          <p class="tg-pool-name">Uniswap V4 — WETH-EAT</p>
          <div class="tg-details">
            <div class="tg-detail">
              <span class="tg-label">APY</span>
              <span class="tg-value positive">17.9%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tg-detail">
              <span class="tg-label">TVL</span>
              <span class="tg-value">$2.3M</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tg-detail">
              <span class="tg-label">Risk</span>
              <span class="tg-value speculative">🟠 Speculative</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tg-detail">
              <span class="tg-label">7d Trend</span>
              <span class="tg-value negative">↓ 16.4%</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tg-meta">Base · LP / Yield Farming</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="tg-mockup">
        <div class="tg-header">
          <span class="tg-bot-name">YieldRadar Bot</span>
          <span class="tg-badge-danger">⚠ FLAGGED</span>
        </div>
        <div class="tg-message">
          <p class="tg-pool-name">Raydium — WSOL-RAY</p>
          <div class="tg-details">
            <div class="tg-detail">
              <span class="tg-label">APY</span>
              <span class="tg-value positive">47.1%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tg-detail">
              <span class="tg-label">TVL</span>
              <span class="tg-value danger">$1.1M</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tg-detail">
              <span class="tg-label">Risk</span>
              <span class="tg-value danger">🔴 Danger</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tg-detail">
              <span class="tg-label">7d Trend</span>
              <span class="tg-value negative">↑ volatile</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tg-meta">Solana · LP — Low TVL, extreme APY, memecoin pair</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="preview-note">Live data from DeFiLlama · Updated every 5 minutes · Pools filtered and scored in real-time</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="getting-started" id="start">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <h2>Get started in 30 seconds</h2>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <span class="step-number">1</span>
        <h3>Open Telegram</h3>
        <p>Search for <strong>@yieldradar_bot</strong> or tap the button below.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <span class="step-number">2</span>
        <h3>Run /start</h3>
        <p>Tell us your preferred chains, risk tolerance, and how often you want alerts.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <span class="step-number">3</span>
        <h3>Done</h3>
        <p>You'll start receiving yield opportunities matched to your criteria. No wallet needed. No KYC. No sign-up.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <a href="https://t.me/yieldradar_bot" class="cta-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      Open in Telegram →
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="chains" id="chains">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <h2>Chain coverage</h2>
    <p class="lead">Monitoring pools across 6 chains — covering over 75% of all DeFi TVL.</p>
    <div class="chain-grid">
      <div class="chain-badge"><span class="chain-dot" style="background:#627EEA"></span>Ethereum</div>
      <div class="chain-badge"><span class="chain-dot" style="background:#0052FF"></span>Base</div>
      <div class="chain-badge"><span class="chain-dot" style="background:#14F195"></span>Solana</div>
      <div class="chain-badge"><span class="chain-dot" style="background:#28A0F0"></span>Arbitrum</div>
      <div class="chain-badge"><span class="chain-dot" style="background:#F0B90B"></span>BSC</div>
      <div class="chain-badge"><span class="chain-dot" style="background:#8247E5"></span>Polygon</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="pricing" id="pricing">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <h2>Pricing</h2>
    <div class="pricing-grid">
      <div class="pricing-card">
        <h3>Free</h3>
        <div class="price">$0</div>
        <ul>
          <li>3 alerts per day</li>
          <li>Basic chain and risk filters</li>
          <li>Daily digest</li>
          <li>All 6 chains</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://t.me/yieldradar_bot" class="cta-secondary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Get started →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="pricing-card pricing-pro">
        <span class="pro-badge">Pro</span>
        <h3>Unlimited</h3>
        <div class="price"><span class="price-original">$14.99</span> $9.99<span class="price-unit">/mo</span></div>
        <p class="price-note">Launch price — locks in forever for early adopters</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Unlimited alerts</li>
          <li>Custom filter rules</li>
          <li>Min TVL and risk thresholds</li>
          <li>7d / 30d APY trend data</li>
          <li>Volatility &amp; decay tracking</li>
          <li>Priority discovery</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://t.me/yieldradar_bot" class="cta-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Subscribe →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="pricing-card">
        <span class="power-badge">Power</span>
        <h3>Analytics</h3>
        <div class="price">$29.99<span class="price-unit">/mo</span></div>
        <p class="price-note">Coming soon</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Everything in Pro</li>
          <li>Yield collapse prediction</li>
          <li>Social sentiment signals</li>
          <li>API access</li>
          <li>Data export</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://t.me/yieldradar_bot" class="cta-cta-disabled" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="pointer-events: none; opacity: 0.5;">Coming soon</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="security" id="security">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <h2>Security</h2>
    <div class="trust-grid">
      <div class="trust-item">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
        <h3>Non-custodial</h3>
        <p>We never touch your funds. No wallet connection, no private keys, no approvals.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="trust-item">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/></svg>
        <h3>GoPlus security checks</h3>
        <p>Every token is scanned for honeypot patterns, malicious contracts, and high-tax mechanisms.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="trust-item">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 0C5.37 0 0 5.37 0 12c0 5.31 3.435 9.795 8.205 11.385.6.105.825-.255.825-.57 0-.285-.015-1.23-.015-2.235-3.015.555-3.795-.735-4.035-1.41-.135-.345-.72-1.41-1.23-1.695-.42-.225-1.02-.78-.015-.795.945-.015 1.62.87 1.845 1.23 1.08 1.815 2.805 1.305 3.495.99.105-.78.42-1.305.765-1.605-2.67-.3-5.46-1.335-5.46-5.925 0-1.305.465-2.385 1.23-3.225-.12-.3-.54-1.53.12-3.18 0 0 1.005-.315 3.3 1.23.96-.27 1.98-.405 3-.405s2.04.135 3 .405c2.295-1.56 3.3-1.23 3.3-1.23.66 1.65.24 2.88.12 3.18.765.84 1.23 1.905 1.23 3.225 0 4.605-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.925.435.375.81 1.095.81 2.22 0 1.605-.015 2.895-.015 3.3 0 .315.225.69.825.57A12.02 12.02 0 0024 12c0-6.63-5.37-12-12-12z"/></svg>
        <h3>Open source</h3>
        <p>Code is public on <a href="https://github.com/goncalovelosa/yield-radar" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color: var(--color-primary); text-decoration: underline;">GitHub</a>. Audit it, self-host it, fork it. No black boxes.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="trust-item">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M8 21h8m-4-4v4"/></svg>
        <h3>Self-hostable</h3>
        <p>Run your own instance with Docker on a $5 VPS. Full control, full privacy.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="moat" id="moat">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <h2>Not just another DeFiLlama wrapper</h2>
    <p class="lead">
      "I could build this in a weekend." — Maybe the v0.1. Here's what you'd miss.
    </p>
    <div class="trust-grid">
      <div class="trust-item">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
        <h3>Historical data advantage</h3>
        <p>Months of APY snapshots and trend data across 18K pools. A weekend project starts from zero — we've been collecting since March 2026.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="trust-item">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"/></svg>
        <h3>Continuous scoring refinement</h3>
        <p>The risk model improves with every cycle. Pool outcomes feed back into weight tuning — the scoring gets better as we collect more data.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="trust-item">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/></svg>
        <h3>Deep security integration</h3>
        <p>GoPlus isn't a checkbox — it's a weighted factor in the composite score. Token security directly impacts your risk rating, not just a pass/fail badge.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="trust-item">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z"/></svg>
        <h3>Protocol-level intelligence</h3>
        <p>We enrich pool data with DeFiLlama protocol metadata — TVL, audit status, protocol age. Most yield tools only look at the pool, not the protocol behind it.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="roadmap" id="roadmap">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <h2>Roadmap</h2>
    <p class="lead">What we've built and what's coming next.</p>
    <div class="roadmap-grid">
      <div class="roadmap-column">
        <h3>✅ Shipped (v1.0–v1.1)</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Multi-factor risk scoring (0–100)</li>
          <li>GoPlus token security scanning</li>
          <li>DeFiLlama protocol metadata enrichment</li>
          <li>7d / 30d APY history &amp; trend analytics</li>
          <li>Telegram Stars subscription payments</li>
          <li>Onboarding, alerts, digest, deep-dive, settings</li>
          <li>Docker deployment with health monitoring</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="roadmap-column">
        <h3>🔄 Next up (v1.2)</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Expanded chains: Optimism, Avalanche, Hyperliquid, Sui</li>
          <li>Launch pricing — $9.99/mo (locks in forever)</li>
          <li>Scoring track record &amp; backtesting dashboard</li>
          <li>Alert quality improvements based on user feedback</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="roadmap-column">
        <h3>🔮 Planned (v2.0)</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Yield collapse prediction (LSTM anomaly detection)</li>
          <li>Social sentiment signals (crypto Twitter / Reddit)</li>
          <li>REST API access (Power tier)</li>
          <li>Data export (CSV / JSON)</li>
          <li>Protocol exploit tracking (REKT database)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="roadmap-column">
        <h3>🚀 Future</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Web dashboard for portfolio monitoring</li>
          <li>Community watchlists &amp; shared filters</li>
          <li>Cross-chain yield arbitrage detection</li>
          <li>Non-custodial position tracking</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="roadmap-cta">
      Have a feature request?
      <a href="https://github.com/goncalovelosa/yield-radar/issues/new" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color: var(--color-primary); text-decoration: underline;">Open an issue on GitHub</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
